{"id":"c6f8346c-1128-4869-a2ae-abef55f1512c","name":"Beyond the Candle: Caelon","description":"<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>Caelon</strong></span></h1><p style=\"text-align: center;\">You watch the blue ember unfold, it happens all too faster, you even don't have time to process the strange event tha——</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 64, 167); color: inherit;\">WELCOME TO CAELON USER</mark></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 248, 255);\"><strong>.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Mold the world and your story in your own way with your floating system panel displaying your statistics!</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Who you was in the past life its up to you. EVERYTHING here is up to you.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: white;\"><strong>⌁⌁</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 240);\"><strong>※</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(245, 196, 239);\"><strong>=</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(232, 183, 242);\"><strong>=※</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(206, 155, 247);\"><strong>=⁛</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(194, 141, 249);\"><strong>※⁛</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(206, 155, 247);\"><strong>=※</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(232, 183, 242);\"><strong>=</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(245, 196, 239);\"><strong>=</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 214, 235);\"><strong>※⌁</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 240);\"><strong>⌁</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(199, 121, 255);\"><strong>Powerful Figures in this world:</strong></span></p><p>📖 <span style=\"color: rgb(15, 255, 0);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(49, 121, 31); color: inherit;\">Sages</mark></strong></span>: master scholars, powerful, but usually don't like fighting. They're usually archivers, researchers, etc.</p><p>🪄 <span style=\"color: rgb(75, 0, 255);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(168, 81, 255); color: inherit;\">Archmages</mark></strong></span>: masters of enchanting and spellcasting with high MP and low HP stats.</p><p>⚔️ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(97, 97, 97); color: inherit;\">Archknights</mark></strong></span>: masters of martial and weapon arts with low MP and high HP stats.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: white;\"><strong>⌁⌁</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 240);\"><strong>※</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(245, 196, 239);\"><strong>=</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(232, 183, 242);\"><strong>=※</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(206, 155, 247);\"><strong>=⁛</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(194, 141, 249);\"><strong>※⁛</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(206, 155, 247);\"><strong>=※</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(232, 183, 242);\"><strong>=</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(245, 196, 239);\"><strong>=</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 214, 235);\"><strong>※⌁</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 240);\"><strong>⌁</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(199, 121, 255);\"><strong>Weapons, Clothing, Powers and Creatures Ranking System:</strong></span></p><p>🧿 <span style=\"color: rgb(201, 177, 147);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(82, 66, 66); color: inherit;\">F</mark></strong></span>: Basic equipment and weak powers. Struggle with minor challenges. ↓</p><p>🟠 <span style=\"color: rgb(249, 102, 0);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(110, 77, 60); color: inherit;\">E</mark></strong></span>: Standard gear and growing abilities. Handle simple tasks. ↓</p><p>🔘 <span style=\"color: rgb(203, 202, 202);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(122, 122, 122); color: inherit;\">D</mark></strong></span>: Reliable tools and decent skills. 